From Andrew Infante Subject Re Countersteering sans Hands In article C C Richard Clarke writes So how do I steer when my hands aren't on the bars Open Budweiser in left hand Camel cigarette in the right no feet If I lean and the bike turns am I countersteering Is countersteering like benchracing only with a taller seat so your feet aren't on the floor Rick Now while I wouldn't recommend doing this while moving Maybe Mike Beaverton can complain to you awhile you might not want to countersteer if you're just sitting in the sounds of Rick falling off bike muttering Damn coulda sworn that's how they told me in the MSF course Andy Infante You can listen to what everybody says but the fact remains ' BMW that you've got to get out there and do the thing DoD Joan Sutherland My opinions dammit have nothing to do with anyone else